        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 11 at 4:52PM EDT by NWS Peachtree City GA</headline>
        <description>At 452 PM EDT, a strong thunderstorm was over Snellville, or near
Lawrenceville, moving southeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Pea sized hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to exposed surfaces is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Snellville, Loganville, Between, Youth, Grayson, Rosebud,
Lawrenceville, and Walnut Grove.
</description>
        <instruction>People outdoors should seek shelter immediately.</instruction>
